result.title: Wierd TLE for Dijkstra
result.content:
In this problem I had to implement Dijkstra. But for some wierd reason this submission gives TLE on 19 test case, but for this one it's AC. Only difference between those is in [ q.push({-d[y],y}) ] (TLE doesn't have -d[y], it has d[y])

Why is this TLE?
